modName: Save Game File - Lehna - Level 2 Ningheim
summary: This is another Ningheim character I made. I wanted to share it. No quests have been started and she is still in Helgen Keep.
descriptionHtml:
Lehna is my second Ningheim Race character. I spent a long time on her face and I am quite happy with the result. She is a fresh level 1 game with no quests started. I am still very new to modding, so input is always great to hear!

I hope you have fun as Lehna!

The following mods are REQUIRED for her to work properly:

ApachiiSkyHair
The Ningheim Race
Brows - Ningheim Addon
More Freckles by Zhoken
RANs Hair
The Eyes of Beauty
Detailed Faces v2
No More Blocky Faces

I hope you enjoy!
author: fishcar
